        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "1481216266545922139",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T09:04:37.612+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Great!\n\nYes, these 6 configurations sound sensible. I'm sure there will be a slot on Run 2 to put even more configurations for silicon testing \ud83d\ude09\nLet me know when you have created the repository, so that I can take a look and add it to open_pdks as an optional library \ud83d\udc4d",
